reviewText: If you are looking at this right now, you just rediscovered the one Disney TV show from your 90's childhood you forgot about for over 15 years.

My first daughter loved these years ago when she was little (and still does at 12)!!!  Now my younger daughter needed her own copy!!!
Not only are these Princess Collection videos entertaining for them, they also teach some important values and manners!
I recommend the entire series!
Way to go Disney!  You are the best!!!
